description:
Dianetics: The Original Thesis (Audiobook CD)

Described by Scientology as "The first formal record of Mr. Hubbard&#039;s researches on
the function of the human mind. Contains the original thesis on his work and explains the ideas which formed the basis of his research." This collection of CDs contains over 9000 minutes of soothing Scientology material. If you misunderstand any of these words, make sure to word-clear them using this handy dictionary:
